                            <comment id="14480304" author="paulk" created="Wed, 29 May 2013 15:59:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It affects both directions actually. Just one example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def list = [1, 3.4, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//.withDefault{ 42 }
&lt;/span&gt;def sub = list[0..1]
sub[3] = 42
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; sub == [1, 3.4, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;, 42]
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; list == [1, 3.4, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;, 42, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
